title: Chris Cagle - Anywhere But Here (192Kbs) (2005)
description:
Anywhere But Here is the third album by country music artist Chris Cagle. Its title track was previously recorded by Brice Long, whose version was a minor chart hit a year prior to the release of Cagle&#039;s version as a single. Also contained on this album are the singles "Miss Me Baby" and "Wal-Mart Parking Lot".
